  "text": "Nonnegative Matrix Tri-Factorization have been proposed in [CITATION_1] .Using the similar method, suppose we have M microblogs and N users, We denote by f U i ,the feature vector which characterizes the demographic information of user i ,then the assumption can be embodied by the adjacency matrix on user as follows,",
